quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,Mayee Waxaan ku dhaartay halkay xiddiguhu ku dhacaan
  56,76,"Oo xaqiiq, waa dhaar dhabtii and u weyn, haddii aad ogaan lahaydeen"
  56,77,Hubaal waa Qur'aan Sharaf Badan
  56,78,Ku yaal Kitaab aad la dhowray
  56,79,Cidina taaban kuwa la daahiriyey mooyee
  56,80,Ah soo waxyoodka Rabbiga uunanka
  56,81,Ee ma warkan baad haddaba u qaadataan wax fudud aan qiimo lahayn
  56,82,oo ka yeeshaan risiqiinna inaad ka been sheegtaan
  56,83,Ee maxaydaan haddaba marka ay (naftu) dhuunta soo gaadho
  56,84,Oo idinku markaas aad eegaysaan
  56,85,"Oo Annagu aan idiinka dhow nahay, laakiinse aydaan arkaynin"
  56,86,Ee Maxaydaan haddaba haddii aad tihiin kuwo aan xil qabanayn
  56,87,Ugu soo celin (weydeen) nafta (jirkeedii) haddii aad run sheegeysaan
  56,88,Haddaba haddii uu ka mid yahay kuwa loo soo dhoweeyo (Allaah)
  56,89,"Markaas waa farax, iyo risiq, iyo Beer barwaaqo ah"
  56,90,Oo haddii uu ka mid yahay kuwa ah gacanta midig
  56,91,Nabad baa kaaga sugnaatay xagga kuwa ah gacanta midig
  56,92,"Haddiise uu ka mid yahay kuwa (Xaqa) diida , habowsanaaysaha ah"
  56,93,Waxaa lagu sooryeen biyo kulul oo karaya
  56,94,Iyo ku gubasho Dabka
  56,95,"Hubaal, arrinkani waa run la hubo"
  56,96,"Ee xurmee Magaca Rabbigaa,Weynaha"